.head 3 +  ! Function: NewUpdateRoyaltyOwnerTotal
.head 4 -  Description: To update the total royalties due to a royalty owner by crediting or debiting
it when we are invoicing with the amount we need to pay the owner for.
Should be able to do cultivar and royalty in one section - need to worry
about whether the customer is Callahans (in this case FNA customers are 
treated normally eg they only have to pay the whole FMN portion), or 
whether the customer is an FMN customer in which case they dont need to pay
the FMN portion, or if the customer owns the royalty himself in which case the royalty owner id will be
inhis customer master royalty owner code, or whether the customer is an FNA customer -
if so then at the moment they have the FMN and FNA portions added and divided by 2
to get the FMN portion that they pay - note nDebitRoy takes off from the
royalty owners total eg crediting trees - nCreditRoy adds to the royalty
owners total eg invoicing a customer  
